ockquote><br />\n唔明，佢整咗兩三日？"},{"pid":"2d4f19ef2057b55ebc8c83522b5cc34806178aa4","tid":354614,"uid":131780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能我細膽，我望住一陣就會成身起晒雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個有個整lift cctv既工人定格影左佢個樣 有2-3日果格cctv keep住見到佢碌大隻整cctv個樣</blockquote><br />\n唔明，佢整咗兩三日？</blockquote><br />\n佢整緊既時候 個cctv錄影左一下 個畫面如是者hold左2-3日 3日後先回復正常錄影"},{"pid":"6dfc0b271eeb98f6ac5b97ae83de099ac64d2830","tid":354614,"uid":14055,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQJlRhGS8L14I7ZuDRea7H0rOrh8xdoup3Lz7oJMpwyKjMbYwTy-w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQJlRhGS8L14I7ZuDRea7H0rOrh8xdoup3Lz7oJMpwyKjMbYwTy-w&h=dd9c0243&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73f812921e97754a74f9398a71496b588c08187c","tid":354614,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能我細膽，我望住一陣就會成身起晒雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個有個整lift cctv既工人定格影左佢個樣 有2-3日果格cctv keep住見到佢碌大隻整cctv個樣</blockquote><br />\n唔明，佢整咗兩三日？</blockquote><br />\n佢整緊既時候 個cctv錄影左一下 個畫面如是者hold左2-3日 3日後先回復正常錄影</blockquote><br />\n起碼唔係影到個陌生而恐怖嘅面孔，其實依定周圍都係天眼，影到靈異嘢嘅機率真係好高，有時返睇自己屋企嘅眼仔，個心都嘭嘭跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d104b7f0c0fb22cd9fee1695c5004866980ed4","tid":354614,"uid":14055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:23:34.000Z","msg":"有聽過有朋友翻睇自己屋企深夜個眼仔錄象，會見到深夜三四點準時係咁專方向，因為佢開咗人臉追蹤功能，但隻眼仔轉動嘅時候係冇「人」行緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10bd656bda7661b32c86ded03b585260e4aa2af","tid":354614,"uid":14055